msgstr "CS Forcé"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "CS:"
msgstr "CS :"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Circle Size (higher number = smaller circles)."
msgstr "Taille des cercles (nombre plus élevé = cercles plus petits)."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "AR Override"
msgstr "AR Forcé"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "AR:"
msgstr "AR :"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Approach Rate (higher number = faster circles)."
msgstr "Taux d'approche (nombre plus élevé = cercles plus rapides)."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "OD Override"
msgstr "OD Forcé"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "OD:"
msgstr "OD :"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Overall Difficulty (higher number = harder accuracy)."
msgstr "Difficulté générale (nombre plus élevé = précision plus difficile)."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "HP Override"
msgstr "HP Forcés"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "HP:"
msgstr "HP :"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Hit/Health Points (higher number = harder survival)."
msgstr "Points de vie (nombre plus élevé = survie plus difficile)."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Speed/BPM Multiplier"
msgstr "Multiplicateur de vitesse/BPM"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid " Experimental Mods (!)"
msgstr " Mods expérimentaux (!)"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Flip Up/Down"
msgstr "Retourner haut/bas"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Playfield is flipped upside down (mirrored at horizontal axis)."
msgstr "L'aire de jeu est retournée (miroir horizontal)."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Flip Left/Right"
msgstr "Retourner gauche/droite"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Playfield is flipped left/right (mirrored at vertical axis)."
msgstr "L'aire de jeu est retournée latéralement (miroir vertical)."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Singletap"
msgstr "Singletap"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "You can only press one key."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez appuyer que sur une seule touche."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Alternate"
msgstr "Alternate"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "You can never use the same key twice in a row."
msgstr "Vous ne pouvez jamais utiliser la même touche deux fois de suite."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "No keylock"
msgstr "No keylock"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "You can use 4 keys instead of only 2."
msgstr "Vous pouvez utiliser 4 touches au lieu de 2."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Also click hitcircles when releasing a key."
msgstr "Clique aussi les hitcercles en relâchant une touche."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "DKS"
msgstr "DKS"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Hitcircles are invisible. Good luck if you use this with Hidden!"
msgstr "Les cercles sont invisibles. Bon courage si vous utilisez ceci avec Hidden !"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Traceable"
msgstr "Traceable"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Freeze Frame"
msgstr "Freeze Frame"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Draw all hitobjects in a combo group together. Try it with Hidden for an extra challenge!"
msgstr "Affiche tous les hitobjects d'un groupe de combo ensemble. Essayez avec Hidden pour un défi supplémentaire !"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "No pausing"
msgstr "No pausing"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Pausing is cheating"
msgstr "Mettre en pause, c'est de la triche"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "FPoSu: Strafing"
msgstr "FPoSu : Strafing"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid ""
"Playfield moves in 3D space (see fposu_mod_strafing_...).\n"
"Only works in FPoSu mode!"
msgstr ""
"L'aire de jeu se déplace dans l'espace 3D (voir fposu_mod_strafing_...).\n"
"Fonctionne uniquement en mode FPoSu !"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Playfield rotates and moves."
msgstr "L'aire de jeu tourne et se déplace."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Wobble"
msgstr "Wobble"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "AR Wobble"
msgstr "AR Wobble"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Approach rate oscillates between -1 and +1."
msgstr "Le taux d'approche oscille entre -1 et +1."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Approach Different"
msgstr "Approach Different"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid ""
"Customize the approach circle animation.\n"
"See mod_approach_different_style.\n"
"See mod_approach_different_initial_size."
msgstr ""
"Personnalise l'animation du cercle d'approche.\n"
"Voir mod_approach_different_style.\n"
"Voir mod_approach_different_initial_size."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Timewarp"
msgstr "Timewarp"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
#, no-c-format
msgid "Speed increases from 100% to 150% over the course of the beatmap."
msgstr "La vitesse augmente de 100 % à 150 % au cours de la beatmap."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "AR Timewarp"
msgstr "AR Timewarp"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
#, no-c-format
msgid "Approach rate decreases from 100% to 50% over the course of the beatmap."
msgstr "Le taux d'approche diminue de 100 % à 50 % au cours de la beatmap."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Minimize"
msgstr "Minimize"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
#, no-c-format
msgid "Circle size decreases from 100% to 50% over the course of the beatmap."
msgstr "La taille des cercles diminue de 100 % à 50 % au cours de la beatmap."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Fading Cursor"
msgstr "Fading Cursor"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "The cursor fades the higher the combo, becoming invisible at 50."
msgstr "Le curseur s'estompe avec le combo, devenant invisible à 50."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Centered cursor."
msgstr "Curseur centré."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "First Person"
msgstr "First Person"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Massively reduced slider follow circle radius."
msgstr "Rayon du cercle de suivi des sliders considérablement réduit."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Precise sliders"
msgstr "Precise sliders"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Reverse Sliders"
msgstr "Reverse Sliders"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Reverses the direction of all sliders. (Reload beatmap to apply!)"
msgstr "Inverse la direction de tous les sliders. (Rechargez la beatmap pour appliquer !)"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "No 50s"
msgstr "No 50s"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Only 300s or 100s. Try harder."
msgstr "Seulement des 300 ou des 100. Essayez plus dur."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "300 or miss. PF \"lite\""
msgstr "300 ou miss. PF \"lite\""

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "No 100s no 50s"
msgstr "No 100s no 50s"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "MinG3012"
msgstr "MinG3012"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "No 100s. Only 300s or 50s. Git gud."
msgstr "Pas de 100. Seulement des 300 ou des 50. Progressez."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Half Timing Window"
msgstr "Half Timing Window"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "The hit timing window is cut in half. Hit early or perfect (300)."
msgstr "La fenêtre de timing est réduite de moitié. Touchez tôt ou parfaitement (300)."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Go below AR 0. Doubled approach time."
msgstr "Passe sous AR 0. Temps d'approche doublé."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "MillhioreF"
msgstr "MillhioreF"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Mafham"
msgstr "Mafham"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid ""
"Approach rate is set to negative infinity. See the entire beatmap at once.\n"
"Uses very aggressive optimizations to keep the framerate high, you have been warned!"
msgstr ""
"Le taux d'approche est réglé sur l'infini négatif. Voyez toute la beatmap d'un coup.\n"
"Utilise des optimisations très agressives pour garder un framerate élevé, vous êtes prévenu !"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Strict clicks"
msgstr "Strict clicks"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Unnecessary clicks count as misses."
msgstr "Les clics inutiles comptent comme des miss."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Strict Tracking"
msgstr "Strict Tracking"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Leaving sliders in any way counts as a miss and combo break. (Reload beatmap to apply!)"
msgstr "Quitter un slider de quelque façon que ce soit compte comme un miss et une rupture de combo. (Rechargez la beatmap pour appliquer !)"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "WARNING: Score submission will be disabled due to non-vanilla mod selection."
msgstr "ATTENTION : La soumission des scores sera désactivée en raison de la sélection de mods non standards."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "1. Reset All Mods"
msgstr "1. Réinitialiser tous les mods"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "2. Close"
msgstr "2. Fermer"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Reduces overall difficulty - larger circles, more forgiving HP drain, less accuracy required."
msgstr "Réduit la difficulté de manière générale : cercles plus grands, barre de vie plus indulgente et moins de précision requise."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid ""
"You can't fail. No matter what.\n"
"NOTE: To disable drain completely:\n"
"Options > Gameplay > Mechanics > \"Disable HP Drain\"."
msgstr ""
"Impossible d'échouer, quoi que vous fassiez.\n"
"NOTE : Pour désactiver complètement le drain :\n"
"Options > Gameplay > Mechanics > \"Disable HP Drain\"."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Everything just got a bit harder..."
msgstr "Tout devient un petit peu plus compliqué."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Miss a note and fail."
msgstr "Ratez une note et vous échouez."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "SS or quit."
msgstr "Un SS sinon rien."

#. TRANSLATORS: "A E S T H E T I C" is a vaporwave aesthetic meme. This is a joke tooltip for Half Time when Nightcore enjoyer mode is on.
#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "A E S T H E T I C"
msgstr "A E S T H E T I Q U E"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Less zoom."
msgstr "Moins de zoom."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Zoooooooooom."
msgstr "Zoooooooooom."

#. TRANSLATORS: "uguuuuuuuu" is an anime-style meme sound/expression. This is a joke tooltip for Double Time when Nightcore enjoyer mode is on.
#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "uguuuuuuuu"
msgstr "uguuuuuuuu"

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Play with no approach circles and fading notes for a slight score advantage."
msgstr "Jouez sans cercles d'approche et avec des notes qui s'estompent progressivement pour un léger avantage de score."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Restricted view area."
msgstr "Zone de vue restreinte."

#: src/App/Neomod/ModSelector.cpp
msgid "Actual flashlight."
msgstr "Véritable lampe torche."

